    10    月    13    日\r\n                              書  記  官    薛如媛","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CDEV/111%2c%e6%a9%8b%e7%b0%a1%2c717%2c20221013%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CDEV,111,橋簡,717,20221013,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"橋簡","JNO":"717","JDATE":"20221013","JTITLE":"清償借款"}